__fi__ I had a butterfly period , a snake period , a bird period , a fish period , a cave period and finally and definitively , an ant period .
__fi__ By my college years , I was a devoted myrmecologist , a specialist on the biology of ants , but my attention and research continued to make journeys across the great variety of life on Earth in general — including all that it means to us as a species , how little we understand it and how pressing a danger that our activities have created for it .
