__fi__ My choice is the culmination of a lifetime commitment that began with growing up on the Gulf Coast of Alabama , on the Florida peninsula .
__fi__ As far back as I can remember , I was enchanted by the natural beauty of that region and the almost tropical exuberance of the plants and animals that grow there .
