__fi__ The human juggernaut is permanently eroding Earth &apos;s ancient biosphere by a combination of forces that can be summarized by the acronym &quot; &quot; HIPPO , &quot; &quot; the animal hippo .
__fi__ H is for habitat destruction , including climate change forced by greenhouse gases .
__fi__ I is for the invasive species like the fire ants , the zebra mussels , broom grasses and pathogenic bacteria and viruses that are flooding every country , and at an exponential rate — that &apos;s the I.
__fi__ The P , the first one in &quot; &quot; HIPPO , &quot; &quot; is for pollution .
__fi__ The second is for continued population , human population expansion .
__fi__ And the final letter is O , for over-harvesting — driving species into extinction by excessive hunting and fishing .
__fi__ The HIPPO juggernaut we have created , if unabated , is destined — according to the best estimates of ongoing biodiversity research — to reduce half of Earth &apos;s still surviving animal and plant species to extinction or critical endangerment by the end of the century .
