__fi__ Public shaming as a blood sport has to stop , and it &apos;s time for an intervention on the Internet and in our culture .
__fi__ The shift begins with something simple , but it &apos;s not easy .
__fi__ We need to return to a long-held value of compassion — compassion and empathy .
__fi__ Online , we &apos;ve got a compassion deficit , an empathy crisis .
